commit.title: [dune] [doc] Support for building the reference manual with Dune.
commit.message:
[dune] [doc] Support for building the reference manual with Dune.

We call Sphinx, and generate a promoted install file for the refman
package.

The promote trick should go away once Dune has support for commands
that produce full directories as targets.
